ckground-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); widows: 2; orphans: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(180, 95, 6);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体;\">【产品特点】</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); widows: 2; orphans: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(180, 95, 6);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体;\">（1）采用食品级硅胶经特殊工艺制成，无毒、无味、不含致癌物质亚硝胺，安全卫生</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); widows: 2; orphans: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(180, 95, 6);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体;\">（2）空气阀自动透气设计，奶瓶内外压力能自动保持平衡，吸嘴不会吸扁，让宝宝吸吮流畅，同时还可避免因吸入过多空气而引起呕吐或呛奶。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); widows: 2; orphans: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(180, 95, 6);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体;\">（3）除符合国家卫生标准外，亦符合美国FDA及欧洲EN等相关标准。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); widows: 2; orphans: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(180, 95, 6);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体;\">（4）采用双十字孔设计，具有不吸不漏及随婴儿的吸吮力大小自动调节出水量的功效，流量较一般奶嘴大，配上宽口径奶瓶，特别适合当吸水杯或果汁杯使用。宝宝食量大时，本品亦可当奶嘴使用。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); widows: 2; orphans: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(180, 95, 6);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体;\">【使用方法】</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); widows: 2; orphans: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(180, 95, 6);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体;\">使用前清洗干净，并放入水中煮沸消毒，1-2分钟，冲调好奶水后，将奶嘴套入螺