ont></font></span></span></font></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); orphans: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; font-family: \'tahoma arial 宋体 sans-serif\'; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 18px; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><font face=\"Microsoft Yahei\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black;\"><font face=\"Tahoma\"><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 0, 0);\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;\">一、奶嘴特点</strong></span></font></span></span><span style=\"color: black;\">&nbsp;</span></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">1、乳胶制品有弹性，与妈妈乳头相</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black;\">近，有母乳相同的触感。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">2、如同乳房般隆起的设计，使婴儿能</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">张开嘴巴充分达到吸吮运动的目</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">的。</span></span></span></font></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); orphans: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; font-family: \'tahoma arial 宋体 sans-serif\'; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 18px; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><font face=\"Microsoft Yahei\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black;\"><font face=\"Tahoma\"><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 0, 0);\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;\">二、奶嘴选择指导</strong></span><br />\r\nS</font>号奶嘴，</span><span style=\"color: black;\">0-3</span><span style=\"color: black;\"><font face=\"宋体\">个月的宝宝使用</font></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color: black;\">M</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black;\">号奶嘴，3</span><span style=\"color: black;\">-6</span><span style=\"color: black;\"><font face=\"宋体\">个月的宝宝使用</font></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color: black;\">L</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black;\">号奶嘴，</span><span style=\"color: black;\">6</span><span style=\"color: black;\"><font face=\"宋体\">个月以上宝宝使用</font></span><br />\r\n<strong><span style=\"color: black;\">+</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black;\">号奶嘴，</span><span style=\"color: black;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black;\">个月以上宝宝使用</span><span style=\"color: black;\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></font></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); orphans: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; font-family: \'tahoma arial 宋体 sans-serif\'; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 18px; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><font face=\"Microsoft Yahei\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black;\"><font face=\"Tahoma\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><font color=\"#990000\">三、使用注意事项</font></strong><br />\r\n1、切勿将奶嘴长时间放置在直射阳光下，可能会造成变形S</font>号奶嘴。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color: black;\">2、</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black;\">洗净后将奶嘴恢复原状，没有清洗干净常会导致奶嘴提前老化。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color: black;\">3、乳胶奶嘴柔软而富有弹性，与妈妈的乳头相似，但是带天然橡胶所特有的味道，请妈妈购买前谨慎思量哦。</span></span></span></font></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); orphans: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; font-family: \'tahoma arial 宋体 sans-serif\'; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 18px; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><font face=\"Microsoft Yahei\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black;\"><font face=\"Tahoma\"><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 0, 0);\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;\">四、常见问题</strong></span><br />\r\n<strong style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(102, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(153, 0, 0);\">Q:新的奶嘴需要用捅孔针通一下才可以使用吗？</span></span></span></strong><br />\r\nA:奶嘴出厂的时候已经把奶嘴孔和通气孔都通好的，只是经过运输保管陈列，有可能灰尘堵住奶嘴孔和通气孔，如果发现异常可以用通孔针通气以后再使用。</font></span></span></span></span></font></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); orphans: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; font-family: \'tahoma arial 宋体 sans-serif\'; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 18px; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><font face=\"Microsoft Yahei\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black;\"><font face=\"Tahoma\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(153, 0, 0);\">Q:乳胶奶嘴和硅胶奶嘴（母乳实感奶嘴）有什么区别？哪种比较好？</span></span></strong><br />\r\nA:两种材质不同，乳胶外观是黄色的，比较柔软，带有天然橡胶的气味，使用寿命在3周左右；硅胶奶嘴无色无味，不易老化，使用寿命在2个月左右。两种各有优点，可以根据自身的喜好选择。</font></span></span></span></span></font></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); orphans: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; font-family: \'tahoma arial 宋体 sans-serif\'; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 18px; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><font face=\"Microsoft Yahei\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black;\"><font face=\"Tahoma\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(153, 0, 0);\">Q:奶嘴在使用一定时期后内部出现白点是什么原因？</span></span></strong><br />\r\nA:奶嘴上附着的白色颗粒，是因为牛奶中的脂肪附着在上面起了变化引起，一旦生成颗粒，无法清洗去除，所以并非奶嘴质量问题。</font></span></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black;\"><font face=\"Tahoma\"><br />\r\n<strong style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(153, 0, 0);\">Q:奶嘴该如何正确消毒？</span></span></strong><br />\r\nA:一般使用的是蒸汽消毒或煮沸消毒2种方法，奶嘴、塑料配件水烧开以后下锅，注意不要贴着锅壁以免引起变形。水烧开以后3、5分钟可以起到消毒作用。</font></span></span></span></span></font></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); orphans: 2; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\"><span style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; font-family: \'tahoma arial 宋体 sans-serif\'; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 18px; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'microsoft yahe